	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64176289"><p>It isn't that there isn't enough power available to heat the batteries up enough, it's that the heating system isn't capable of enough power.</p><p>Let's say that you need 5 kWh to warm the battery up.  But in the current conditions, the battery is radiating 1kW.  A 11kW heater would have you warmed up in 30 minutes, but if you only have a 1.2kW heater, you're going to be there for a while.</p><p>Options include increasing the wattage of the heaters or insulating the battery more.  Maybe a battery blanket like used by ma<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64176289">

